      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Reader responses to articles on teens in adult prisons and portrayal of Hillary Clinton (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Many readers of our cover article on teenagers doing time in adult prisons were shocked at the thought of hardened criminals serving as stand-in parents for these adolescent inmates. And Hillary Clinton a bluestocking? Some said that she has clouded rather than illuminated feminist issues.</p>
      </block>
